                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I don't think shards are in the game to balance anything, I think they're designed to make more interesting and harder decisions for Warlocks to make in battle. It's basically a limit on certain types of abilities so you use them more sparingly, and that makes those choices more interesting then regular spells.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />1010011010 - Binary of the Beast!</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
                </table></td>
        </tr>
